<plot>A beautiful singer, Maria Malibran (Maria Cebotaria), is forced to turn to the stage after her husband takes to gambling, and goes to Paris where she falls in love with a famous violinist. When her money-seeking husband reappears, the couple go to London, where they find happiness. A composer falls in love with Maria but when his affections are unrequited, he becomes broken, takes to drinking and dies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357877</url></doc>
